e classroom, laser device) enhances authenticity and supports the commentary", "Relevant supporting explanations are offered for each object\u00e2\u0080\u0099s contribution, maintaining a coherent narrative with minimal repetition", "The exact IA prompt is clearly stated at the outset, keeping the exhibition focused on the prescribed knowledge question"], "weaknesses": ["Some scientific claims (eg. JWST questioning the Big Bang) lack citation or detailed evidence, reducing precision", "TOK terminology (shared vs personal knowledge, ways of knowing) is used only implicitly rather than explicitly framed", "Introduction lacks a concise thesis to guide the structure and connect objects to the knowledge question", "Certain sections end abruptly or appear incomplete, and the overall conclusion is missing to synthesize the analysis", "Explanations of how the diffraction experiment and marker example produce new knowledge are anecdotal and would benefit from deeper evidential support"], "calculationMethod": "Holistic AI evaluation: The exhibition meets the descriptor for the 7\u00e2\u0080\u00938 band by clearly identifying three specific, real-world objects and explaining their relevance to the IA prompt with sustained, coherent commentary. Many points are supported by appropriate details and references to the prompt, and the authentic photographs enhance credibility. However, gaps in precision\u00e2\u0080\u0094such as unsubstantiated scientific assertions, incomplete integration of TOK terminology, and the absence of a guiding thesis and concluding synthesis\u00e2\u0080\u0094prevent the work from reaching the highest 9\u00e2\u0080\u009310 band. An 8 reflects strong overall performance with room for deeper analysis and more rigorous evidential support.", "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}], "strandSelections": [{"versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "strandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "selectedBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "bandScore": 8, "reasoning": "$49"}], "annotations": [{"id": "a316d248-9b59-4583-8a0c-8e77aef5ce86", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.0686, "width": 0.8319, "height": 0.04630000000000001}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.0686}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.0686}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.1149}, {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.1149}], "comment": "The phrase \u00e2\u0080\u009cCosmic Dawn\u00e2\u0080\u009d appears without definition or connection to the prompt. The student should clarify this term and explain its relevance to how the JWST expands knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "b31de9dc-92e0-484d-bb0b-3c8477b74173", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.5668, "width": 0.323, "height": 0.019100000000000006}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.5668}, {"x": 0.4137, "y": 0.5668}, {"x": 0.4137, "y": 0.5859}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.5859}], "comment": "The title \u00e2\u0080\u009cObject 1: James Webb Space Telescope\u00e2\u0080\u009d clearly identifies the first real-world object and sets precise context by naming the instrument and its function.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "c43a5aa4-8bfc-41cc-a294-7d0c019fecac", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.0686, "width": 0.8331, "height": 0.20429999999999998}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.0686}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.0686}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.2729}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.2729}], "comment": "The diffraction experiment is described procedurally but lacks an explicit link to how it generated novel insight. The student should explain why observing interference patterns constitutes knowledge production.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "aa4a31f6-ba56-4b19-9c7e-18c063c8993e", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1039, "y": 0.3277, "width": 0.3419, "height": 0.32320000000000004}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1039, "y": 0.3277}, {"x": 0.4458, "y": 0.3277}, {"x": 0.4458, "y": 0.6509}, {"x": 0.1039, "y": 0.6509}], "comment": "Presenting a photograph of the actual classroom marker enhances authenticity by grounding the object in a real-world educational context\u00e2\u0080\u0094an important strength in the exhibition.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "817c7948-e083-4493-a47d-c4454c03c9d3", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.8829, "width": 0.8318, "height": 0.04410000000000003}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.8829}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.8829}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.927}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.927}], "comment": "The sentence is incomplete and leaves the argument hanging. The student must finish the thought about which galaxies were observed and explain why their existence challenges existing models.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "67801934-81cf-4446-92a1-237733167b0e", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1618, "y": 0.11, "width": 0.6776, "height": 0.01870000000000001}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1618, "y": 0.11}, {"x": 0.8394, "y": 0.11}, {"x": 0.8394, "y": 0.1287}, {"x": 0.1618, "y": 0.1287}], "comment": "The student clearly states the exact IA prompt at the outset, ensuring the exhibition remains focused on the prescribed knowledge question about material tools.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "3a9ecb58-3af1-4dbf-b17a-8da5299a40f4", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.2168, "width": 0.8318, "height": 0.122}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.2168}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.2168}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.3388}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.3388}], "comment": "The introduction outlines the plan but lacks a concise thesis or guiding argument that explicitly connects each object to the prompt\u00e2\u0080\u0099s knowledge question. The student should articulate a clear thesis statement to guide the exhibition\u00e2\u0080\u0099s structure.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "1ba508e7-9dc0-48ca-971f-df49006cf56f", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.7778, "width": 0.8318, "height": 0.07079999999999997}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.7778}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.7778}, {"x": 0.9225, "y": 0.8486}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.8486}], "comment": "The statement \u00e2\u0080\u009cthe Big Bang theory was established\u00e2\u0080\u009d is unsubstantiated. The student should cite specific historical or scientific sources to support this claim and show how material tools contributed to its development.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d71906d5-1510-4c15-8061-bf103b421a6b", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0989, "y": 0.3598, "width": 0.4011, "height": 0.16779999999999995}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0989, "y": 0.3598}, {"x": 0.5, "y": 0.3598}, {"x": 0.5, "y": 0.5276}, {"x": 0.0989, "y": 0.5276}], "comment": "Although the illustration of the JWST is vivid, the student does not integrate this image into the verbal commentary. They should explicitly reference the visual aid\u00e2\u0080\u0099s role in knowledge production in the accompanying analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "0c3c1ea4-7d4f-498c-9e76-3045bfc664d0", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.6189, "width": 0.8337, "height": 0.1251}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.6189}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.6189}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.744}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.744}], "comment": "The description of cosmology is engaging but largely narrative. To strengthen the TOK analysis, the student should link these observations directly to knowledge-production concepts like shared vs. personal knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "819a3413-4332-4c48-bcf8-2afb2e4aa89f", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.1487, "width": 0.8325, "height": 0.1501}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.1487}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.1487}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.2988}, {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.2988}], "comment": "This paragraph reiterates earlier points about questioning assumptions. Rather than repeating, the student could deepen the analysis by exploring how specific JWST discoveries reshaped cosmological models.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "a30656bd-313c-4329-8a79-3db42c6d070e", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.1487, "width": 0.8325, "height": 0.1501}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.1487}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.1487}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.2988}, {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.2988}], "comment": "This discussion remains surface-level. The student should integrate TOK terminology (e.g., shared knowledge, ways of knowing) to analyze how the marker mediates language learning beyond mere visualization.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "60babbdd-cdba-4dc6-bb48-d7752db53671", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.6906, "width": 0.2368, "height": 0.019100000000000006}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.6906}, {"x": 0.3287, "y": 0.6906}, {"x": 0.3287, "y": 0.7097}, {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.7097}], "comment": "The title \u00e2\u0080\u009cObject 2: blackboard marker\u00e2\u0080\u009d succinctly identifies the second object and signals its classroom context immediately.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "ad4d7475-e636-4f30-9f2a-3fb5c9c854c1", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.744, "width": 0.8325, "height": 0.14959999999999996}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.744}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.744}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.8936}, {"x": 0.0919, "y": 0.8936}], "comment": "The justification is anecdotal and descriptive. To bolster the link to the prompt, the student should provide concrete examples or studies demonstrating how visual tools facilitate language acquisition.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "90d4f7f9-5a89-4670-b7ff-d0a0db11069c", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1045, "y": 0.3268, "width": 0.2992, "height": 0.2841}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1045, "y": 0.3268}, {"x": 0.4037, "y": 0.3268}, {"x": 0.4037, "y": 0.6109}, {"x": 0.1045, "y": 0.6109}], "comment": "Including an image of the laser pointer as an everyday object successfully demonstrates how commonplace tools can have profound scientific applications.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d8727e20-b834-432f-9265-6a54e8b30510", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.3059, "width": 0.8331, "height": 0.12380000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.3059}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.3059}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.4297}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.4297}], "comment": "The discussion of wave-particle duality is scientifically accurate yet isolated. To strengthen the TOK focus, the student should discuss how material tools shape our understanding of complex phenomena.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "1ec13bbf-29b0-486a-b350-c72fbc8ae8d9", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.3059, "width": 0.8331, "height": 0.12380000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.3059}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.3059}, {"x": 0.9238, "y": 0.4297}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.4297}], "comment": "This section ends abruptly with no concluding reflection. The student should add a conclusion that synthesizes the three objects and reaffirms how material tools underpin knowledge acquisition.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "02198fad-03a6-4d60-9f7a-23549c40f41b", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.6509, "width": 0.1391, "height": 0.020100000000000007}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.6509}, {"x": 0.2298, "y": 0.6509}, {"x": 0.2298, "y": 0.671}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.671}], "comment": "The header \u00e2\u0080\u009cObject 3: a laser\u00e2\u0080\u009d clearly signals the third object and primes the reader for the shift to scientific experimentation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "2e477354-3a46-4878-94db-0061c6894487", "versionId": "f3829cda-6089-4cd3-a870-ebdeb6a4e007", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.7039, "width": 0.8337, "height": 0.17770000000000008}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.7039}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.7039}, {"x": 0.9244, "y": 0.8816}, {"x": 0.0907, "y": 0.8816}], "comment": "The narrative about the laser\u00e2\u0080\u0099s origin is personal but does not explain its specific use in a knowledge-production context. The student should describe an actual experiment or demonstration setting.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "181b06d3-cdd8-41e4-915e-6824fdecff19", "title": "How important are material tools in the production or acquisition of knowledge?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-B", "tok", "sl"], "slug": "how-important-are-material-tools-in-the-production-or-2", "isPublic": true, "isPremium": true, "showScores": true, "createdAt": "2025-08-05T08:19:10.381Z", "userSubmissionId": "69ee51e6-d68f-4f32-85d2-9f60c0746604", "submissionId": "3a3219b9-4ff3-4666-a88c-9446691c9609", "similarity": 0.692682971, "normalizedScore": 0.8, "compositeScore": 0.7248780797000001, "matchingFileId": "", "matchingChunkId": "", "matchingChunkNumber": 0, "userSubmission": {"id": "69ee51e6-d68f-4f32-85d2-9f60c0746604", "score": "B", "scoreType": "letter", "level": null, "researchQuestion": null, "tokPrompt": null, "title": "How important are material tools in the production or acquisition of knowledge? ", "cohort": "M25", "createdAt": "2025-07-17T22:40:37.673Z", "subjectId": 582, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "subject": {"id": 582, "title": "Theory of Knowledge (TOK)", "slug": "ib-theory-of-knowledge-tok"}, "rubric": {"id": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-ab